{"tid":1401190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有鬼呀！！！！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T15:53:05.000Z","uid":18914,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"df31af477b6024a89d92f169b524e427700d2813","tid":1401190,"uid":18914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:23:25.000Z","msg":"我唔相信大家會四處破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點樣避免比人屈呀！！屌！"},{"pid":"fe1eb8f88dd4a516182c20b8dcebc9ac0476030c","tid":1401190,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:24:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>仲係度慢慢一二一二做乜撚野呀！</strong></span></span><br />\n屌你見到成班狗衝埋黎仲可以棟係度唔走做乜春野呀！下？<br />\n又唔係第一次出黎，講左幾撚多次be water轉場呀！仲唔走？<br />\n次次都話要尊重前線，你地唔撚識保護自己，見到狗唔撚走到時比狗拉比狗打要其他人點幫你呀！下！<br />\n啲人好心提你地走，你倒轉屌返佢地? 屌你老母呀！屌真係好嬲！"},{"pid":"4a54ecd07dd16a87d5de9094e6b5b4c0a7ac21bc","tid":1401190,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:25:53.000Z","msg":"有條友仲大大聲話警察少人夠打喎！屌你老母唔係要成班手足陪你死呀？"},{"pid":"9200609b98277cef3dd3b308e2f44bebb4ee504c","tid":1401190,"uid":18914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:26:25.000Z","msg":"根本有鬼，佢地搵人滲透好簡單，點樣可以分到/避免受影響呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fd482e5f9cc460cbdc38e86e73bb10a5cbd909","tid":1401190,"uid":18914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:29:30.000Z","msg":"睇電視都感受到件事唔會發展到咁樣，勇武都不至於咁無理智，唔聽人講掛！會累死手足架！係咪真係要捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de45d7744f49c952345de05f4279aef40545e8e","tid":1401190,"uid":18914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a54ecd07dd16a87d5de9094e6b5b4c0a7ac21bc","tid":1401190,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB